* **In Their Words:**
  > "[Verbatim quote — clip-tagged if available]"

## 3. [Theme Name 3]
* **Lived Experience:** [Summary of their perspective written simply and clearly]
* **In Their Words:**
  > "[Verbatim quote — clip-tagged if available]"

